Summary: Spoted severial UFO's over the town of Breezewood, Pennsylvaina, snapped picture.
divs: Sighting DetailsWHILE DRIVING ON ROUTE 30 TOWARD BREEZEWOOD I SPOTED THESE IN THE AIR STOPPED ON THE ROAD AND SNAPPED THESE PICTURES. LATTER I WENT AND HAD THE PICTURES BLOWN UP AT WAL-MART AND FOUND SERVIAL MORE "OBJECTS". I HAVE THE PICTURES AND AM WILLING TO SCAN THEM AND E-MAIL OR SPEAK TO SOMEONE ABOUT THEM. I CANNOT AT THIS TIME CAUSE I AM ON A FRIENDS COMPUTER WITH OUT A SCANNER.
